	.string "My name is {COLOR BLUE}Dr. Colress{COLOR DARK_GRAY} of Unova.\p"
	.string "I've dedicated my life to\n"
	.string "understanding what it is that makes\l"
	.string "Pokémon Trainers powerful.\p"
